<hw>candelabra</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a branched,
ornamental candlestick having several sockets for candles.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> candelabrum.</syn>⟦br⟧
